Mangalore Refinery Seeks to Buy Crude, Sell Gasoil, Jet Fuel

-- B y   P r a t i s h   N a r a y a n a n   a n d   L a n a n h   N g u y e n
-- 
2011-08-18T15:54:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/mangalore-refinery-seeks-to-buy-crude-sell-gasoil-jet-fuel.html
Mangalore Refinery & Petrochemicals
Ltd. (MRPL) , a unit of  India ’s largest explorer, is seeking to buy
600,000 barrels of low-sulfur  crude oil  in October, according to
a tender document seen by Bloomberg News.  The company sought to sell 50,000 metric tons of gasoil and
36,000 tons of  jet fuel  for September loading, according to
separate tender documents seen by Bloomberg.  Details of the tenders are as follows:  Oil & Natural Gas Corp., the country’s largest oil
explorer, owns 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  To contact the reporters on this story:
